'''Chris "Casper" Kelly''' is an American [[writer]], [[television director]], and [[Television producer|producer]].

==Career==

Kelly is best known as the co-creator of the [[Adult Swim]] live-action series ''[[Your Pretty Face Is Going to Hell]]'', the Adult Swim animated series ''[[Stroker and Hoop]]'', and the Adult Swim ''[[Infomercials (TV series)|Infomercials]]'' episode ''[[Too Many Cooks (short)|Too Many Cooks]]'', which he also directed. ''Too Many Cooks'' was released online and went [[Viral video|viral]], amassing over two million views within five days of its release.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Snetiker|first1=Marc|title='Too Many Cooks' creator tries to explain his awesomely bizarre Adult Swim short|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/11/07/adult-swim-too-many-cooks|accessdate=October 24, 2015|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=November 7, 2014}}</ref> He also co-directed and co-wrote another ''Infomercials'' episode in 2018 titled ''Final Deployment 4: Queen Battle Walkthrough'' which parodies [[Video game live streaming|livestreaming gaming]] culture.<ref>{{cite web |last=Marnell |first=Blair |url=https://nerdist.com/final-deployment-4-too-many-cooks-adult-swim/ |title=Too Many Cooks Creator Returns With Mindbending Twitch Streamer Parody |work=Nerdist |date=June 26, 2018 |accessdate=September 8, 2018}}</ref> He has written episodes of ''[[Squidbillies]]'', ''[[Harvey Birdman, Attorney at Law]]'', and ''[[Aqua Teen Hunger Force]]''.

He is also a fiction writer. His book, ''More Stories About Spaceships and Cancer'', a collection of short stories, was published in 2012. His short story, ''The Sensitive Person's Joke Book'', was published in the web literary magazine ''Necessary Fiction''.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kelly|first1=Casper|title=Necessary Fiction - The Sensitive Person's Joke Book|url=http://necessaryfiction.com/stories/CasperKellyTheSensitivePersonsJokeBook|accessdate=October 24, 2015|work=Necessary Fiction|date=September 24, 2011}}</ref>

